e-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-righteousness-al-birr","tag-charity-al-sadaqah","tag-food-al-taam","tag-good-deeds-hasanat","tag-hereafter-akhirah","tag-manners-adab","tag-reward-al-ajr","tag-sheep-al-ghanam"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-8Ye","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":40368,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/06\/05\/life-is-short\/","url_meta":{"origin":34486,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Dunya: Time remaining for the world is short","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty made the world for a short time, and what remains is but the shortest of it. The parable of what remains is like the pure mountaintop water already drank while what is leftover\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19201,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/19\/oath-by-allah-charity-patience\/","url_meta":{"origin":34486,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Character: I swear by Allah on three qualities","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 19, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Kabshah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI swear an oath by Allah on three qualities and I will tell you about them, so memorize them: the wealth of a servant is not decreased by charity, a servant is not wronged by oppression\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2526,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/26\/allah-puts-him-to-action\/","url_meta":{"origin":34486,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Qadr: If Allah intends good, He puts him to action","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 26, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf Allah wills goodness for a servant, He puts him into action.\u201d It was said, \u201cHow is he put into action, O Messenger of Allah?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHe is guided to righteous deeds before\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10895,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/03\/jibreel-aisha-wife-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34486,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Aisha: The Prophet is told Aisha is his wife in Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 3, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: Gabriel came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, with her image on a green, silken cloth and he said, \u201cVerily, this is your wife in this world and in the Hereafter.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3880 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u062c\u0650\u0628\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u064